Donately,is,a,REST,API,that,allows,for,users,to,make,online,donations,Donately,API,provides,a,space,for,non,profits,to,manage,their,donors,and,online,giving,activity,Authentication,is,through,API,token,and,standard,HTTP,and,all,responses,including,errors,are,returned,in,JSON,The,extensive,documentation,of,requests,covers,information,and,administrative,actions,regarding,accounts,people,donations,and,fundraisers,Donately,API,is,a,fee,based,service,that,is,available,for,worldwide,fundraising,transactions